<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٤٩٤٢ - <span class="c2">«كان يذبح أضحيته بيده»</span> .<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
